'''米豬連'''是一個在[[香港|香港]]於[[反對逃犯條例修訂草案運動|反對逃犯條例修訂草案運動]]期間成立的飲食指南，以助消費者識別支持反修例運動的[[黃店|黃店]]<ref name="HKFP-191228">{{cite web |title=In Hong Kong, local entrepreneurs champion the pro-democracy cause |url=https://hongkongfp.com/2019/12/28/hong-kong-local-entrepreneurs-champion-pro-democracy-cause/ |publisher=Hong Kong Free Press |accessdate=2020-07-27 |date=2019-12-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200702062507/https://hongkongfp.com/2019/12/28/hong-kong-local-entrepreneurs-champion-pro-democracy-cause/ |archive-date=2020-07-02 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="文匯報-20191231">{{Cite web|title=入圈陷無底潭 雜費交極唔完|url=http://paper.wenweipo.com/2019/12/31/HK1912310003.htm|accessdate=|author=|date=2019-12-31|format=|work=文匯報 (香港)|publisher=|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191230232856/http://paper.wenweipo.com/2019/12/31/HK1912310003.htm|archive-date=2019-12-30|dead-url=no}}</ref>，其名稱戲仿[[米其林指南|米芝蓮指南]]<ref name="shead-191012"/><ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=網民創作「米豬連」 貼紙推介撐「黃店」|url=http://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/5233658/|accessdate=|author=|date=2019-10-12|format=|work=巴士的報|publisher=|language=zh-hk|archive-date=2021-04-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210418053727/https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/5233658-%e3%80%90%e4%bf%ae%e4%be%8b%e9%a2%a8%e6%b3%a2%e3%80%91%e7%b6%b2%e6%b0%91%e5%89%b5%e4%bd%9c%e3%80%8c%e7%b1%b3%e8%b1%ac%e9%80%a3%e3%80%8d-%e8%b2%bc%e7%b4%99%e6%8e%a8%e4%bb%8b%e6%92%90%e3%80%8c%e9%bb%83|dead-url=no}}</ref>。其[[標誌|標誌]]是一隻戴黃色[[頭盔|頭盔]]的[[連登豬|連豬]]。<ref>{{Cite web|title=米豬連官方網站|url=https://michul.in/|accessdate=|author=|date=|format=|publisher=|language=zh-hk|archive-date=2021-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210121114127/https://michul.in/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 簡介 ==
米豬連是響應網民提倡建立[[黃色經濟圈|黃色經濟圈]]而創立的認證網站<ref name="HK01-200102">{{Cite web|url=https://www.hk01.com/18%E5%8D%80%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/416847/%E9%BB%83%E8%89%B2%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E5%9C%88-%E8%A8%AD%E6%94%B6%E8%B2%BB%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E8%A2%AB%E6%89%B9%E9%A3%9F%E4%BA%BA%E8%A1%80%E9%A5%85%E9%A0%AD-%E6%A6%AE%E5%85%89%E8%81%AF%E7%9B%9Fapp%E8%83%8E%E6%AD%BB%E8%85%B9%E4%B8%AD|title=設收費功能被批食人血饅頭　有「黃色經濟圈」資訊App胎死腹中|date=2020-01-02|work=香港01|accessdate=2020-07-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200105080123/https://www.hk01.com/18%E5%8D%80%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/416847/%E9%BB%83%E8%89%B2%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E5%9C%88-%E8%A8%AD%E6%94%B6%E8%B2%BB%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E8%A2%AB%E6%89%B9%E9%A3%9F%E4%BA%BA%E8%A1%80%E9%A5%85%E9%A0%AD-%E6%A6%AE%E5%85%89%E8%81%AF%E7%9B%9Fapp%E8%83%8E%E6%AD%BB%E8%85%B9%E4%B8%AD|archive-date=2020-01-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>，收錄香港的[[黃店|黃店]]、[[藍店|藍店]]及[[中立|綠店]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.hk01.com/%E9%A3%9F%E7%8E%A9%E8%B2%B7/403994/%E5%BF%85%E8%A9%A6-%E9%BB%83%E8%97%8D%E5%95%86%E6%88%B6%E9%A3%9F%E5%BA%97%E7%B6%B2%E9%A0%81%E6%8E%A8%E4%BB%8B-%E7%B1%B3%E8%B1%AC%E9%80%A3-%E6%96%B0%E6%99%82%E4%BB%A3%E6%B6%88%E8%B2%BB%E5%9C%B0%E5%9C%96%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E6%9B%B4%E5%AE%8C%E5%96%84|title=必試！黃藍商戶食店網頁推介　米豬連、新時代消費地圖功能更完善|date=2019-11-29|work=香港01|accessdate=2020-07-27|archive-date=2021-08-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210803223641/https://www.hk01.com/%E9%A3%9F%E7%8E%A9%E8%B2%B7/403994/%E5%BF%85%E8%A9%A6-%E9%BB%83%E8%97%8D%E5%95%86%E6%88%B6%E9%A3%9F%E5%BA%97%E7%B6%B2%E9%A0%81%E6%8E%A8%E4%BB%8B-%E7%B1%B3%E8%B1%AC%E9%80%A3-%E6%96%B0%E6%99%82%E4%BB%A3%E6%B6%88%E8%B2%BB%E5%9C%B0%E5%9C%96%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E6%9B%B4%E5%AE%8C%E5%96%84|dead-url=no}}</ref>。食肆會把一張米豬連的貼紙貼在店舖的門口，以便食客辨識出是否黃店。貼紙上一般會有一隻[[連豬|連豬]]作為標記，並寫上「幫襯 勁買」等鼓勵人們消費的標語。<ref name="shead-191012">{{Cite web|url=https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1611216/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E5%89%B5%E4%BD%9C-%E7%B1%B3%E8%B1%AC%E9%80%A3-%E8%B2%BC%E7%B4%99%E6%8E%A8%E4%BB%8B%E6%92%90-%E9%BB%83%E5%BA%97|title=【修例風波】網民創作「米豬連」  貼紙推介撐「黃店」|date=2019-10-12|work=頭條日報|accessdate=2020-07-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191012062322/http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1611216/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E5%89%B5%E4%BD%9C-%E7%B1%B3%E8%B1%AC%E9%80%A3-%E8%B2%BC%E7%B4%99%E6%8E%A8%E4%BB%8B%E6%92%90-%E9%BB%83%E5%BA%97|archive-date=2019-10-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>一些餐廳東主認為米豬連標籤有助消費者認清食肆東主的政治立場<ref>{{cite web |title=【抗暴小店】網民創「米豬連」標籤支持黃店 方便同路人搵食 上環「獲頒」Café：可悲產物 |url=https://etw.nextdigital.com.hk/article/3_60169138 |publisher=飲食男女 |accessdate=2020-07-27 |date=2019-10-26 |archive-date=2020-08-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200811085550/https://etw.nextdigital.com.hk/article/3_60169138 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=":0" />。獲米豬連認證的餐廳之中，一些更獲得了[[米芝蓮指南|米芝蓮指南]]推介<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20191218/AXZDRZQWCLPHKFXGVCZJOUTVNI/|title=米豬連奪米芝蓮　上榜5黃店堅持與港人同行|date=2019-12-18|work=蘋果日報 (香港)|accessdate=2020-07-27|archive-date=2021-06-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210621170136/https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20191218/AXZDRZQWCLPHKFXGVCZJOUTVNI/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

米豬連的義工團隊更會協助餐廳登記成為香港立法會飲食界功能組別的選民，其義工團隊於半年間協助愈千間食肆登記。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20200624/s00002/1592936959545/%E8%B8%8F%E9%81%8D%E5%A4%A7%E8%A1%97%E5%B0%8F%E5%B7%B7-%E7%BE%A9%E5%B7%A5%E5%9C%98%E9%9A%8A%E5%8D%8A%E5%B9%B4%E5%8A%A9%E9%80%BE%E5%8D%83%E3%80%8C%E9%BB%83%E5%BA%97%E3%80%8D%E7%99%BB%E8%A8%98|title=踏遍大街小巷  義工團隊半年助逾千「黃店」登記|date=2020-06-24|work=明報|accessdate=2020-07-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200721230329/https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200624/s00002/1592936959545/%e8%b8%8f%e9%81%8d%e5%a4%a7%e8%a1%97%e5%b0%8f%e5%b7%b7-%e7%be%a9%e5%b7%a5%e5%9c%98%e9%9a%8a%e5%8d%8a%e5%b9%b4%e5%8a%a9%e9%80%be%e5%8d%83%e3%80%8c%e9%bb%83%e5%ba%97%e3%80%8d%e7%99%bb%e8%a8%98|archive-date=2020-07-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>米豬連標誌除了用於食肆外，亦會用於宣傳其他與[[黃色經濟圈|黃色經濟圈]]相關的活動，例如年宵<ref>{{cite web |title=房署取消葵涌「和你宵」場地申請 |url=http://paper.wenweipo.com/2020/01/16/YO2001160013.htm |publisher=[[文匯報_(香港)|文匯報 (香港)]] |accessdate=2020-07-27 |date=2020-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200116054959/http://paper.wenweipo.com/2020/01/16/YO2001160013.htm |archive-date=2020-01-16 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

